{"problem":{"stackLimit":128,"modifiedUser":"root","auth":1,"isRemote":false,"description":"<p>一个`n * m`的方格图，一些格子被涂成了黑色，在方格图中被标为1，白色格子标为0。问有多少个四连通的黑色格子连通块。四连通的黑色格子连通块指的是一片由黑色格子组成的区域，其中的每个黑色格子能通过四连通的走法（上下左右），只走黑色格子，到达该联通块中的其它黑色格子。<p>","removeEndBlank":true,"uploadCase":true,"source":"","remote":false,"title":"连通块","type":0,"difficulty":1,"output":"<p>一行一个整数ans，表示图中有ans个黑色格子连通块。<p>","timeLimit":1000,"input":"<p>第一行两个整数n,m(1≤n,m≤100)，表示一个n \\* m的方格图。<p><p>接下来n行，每行m个整数，分别为0或1，表示这个格子是黑色还是白色。<p>","examples":"<input>3 3\n1 1 1\n0 1 0\n1 0 1\n\n</input><output>3\n</output>","ioScore":10000,"codeShare":false,"hint":"","isRemoveEndBlank":true,"openCaseResult":true,"memoryLimit":256,"problemId":"T1335","isUploadCase":true},"languages":["C","C With O2","C++","C++ With O2","Java","Python3","Python2","Golang","C#"],"codeTemplates":[],"isSpj":false,"samples":[{"output":"1.out","input":"1.in","score":100},{"output":"2.out","input":"2.in","score":100},{"output":"3.out","input":"3.in","score":100},{"output":"4.out","input":"4.in","score":100},{"output":"5.out","input":"5.in","score":100},{"output":"6.out","input":"6.in","score":100},{"output":"7.out","input":"7.in","score":100},{"output":"8.out","input":"8.in","score":100},{"output":"9.out","input":"9.in","score":100},{"output":"10.out","input":"10.in","score":100}],"tags":["一本通在线评测"]}